---

This project (MontCoBugs) is a fork of LABugs.org by Rhys Marsh
(https://github.com/rhysmarsh/LAbugs), adapted to cover the butterflies,
dragonflies, and damselflies of Montgomery County, Pennsylvania. The
original application architecture, design, and approach are Rhys Marsh's
work, used here with gratitude under the MIT License above.

Species photographs are sourced from iNaturalist (inaturalist.org) and are
subject to their respective Creative Commons licenses as specified by the
original observers. Species descriptions for MontCo Bugs are original works
by Sam Stuart. Taxonomic data is sourced from the Catalogue of Life, ITIS,
and other public taxonomic databases. Odonate seasonal and habitat data is
informed by the Pennsylvania DCNR Nescopeck State Park dragonfly and
damselfly checklist.